<h4>WELCOME</h4>
<h1>Creating a more informed, empowered and efficient book industry</h1>
The Book Industry Study Group (BISG) is a national, not-for-profit U.S. book trade association with the mission of creating a more informed, empowered and efficient book industry. Weâ€™re committed to the development of effective industry-wide standards, best practices, research and events related to both physical and digital products that enhance relationships between all trading partners.

</div>
